snippet.textDisplay: My daughter asked me the other day while we were watching Hot Ones if I'd go on the show if I was famous. I'm from Minnesota. My favorite food is klub (potato dumplings). I use mild hot sauce. But still, the show is so fascinating that I'd have to consider it (as long as the milk is ever-flowing). And I never watch celebrity interviews; these are just so real and cool. Great job, Sean and company!
